<i>Maddie and Chloe</i>
<i>will go head to head.</i>

00:00:06.539 --> 00:00:10.310 line:5%,start
CATHY: We have our nemesis here again.

00:00:10.377 --> 00:00:12.579 line:5%,start
The Abby Lee Dance Company, boo.

00:00:12.645 --> 00:00:13.480 line:5%,start
Where's Brooke?

00:00:13.546 --> 00:00:15.015 line:5%,start
I don't think she's coming this weekend.

00:00:15.081 --> 00:00:16.683 line:5%,start
You're dismissed, you're dismissed.

00:00:16.750 --> 00:00:18.251 line:5%,start
There will be no group dance this week.

00:00:18.318 --> 00:00:19.152 line:5%,start
That's it.

00:00:19.219 --> 00:00:21.221 line:5%,start
ANNOUNCER: <i>And our top soloist--</i>

00:00:21.287 --> 00:00:24.991 line:5%,start
<i>Chloe from Abby Lee Dance.</i>

00:00:25.058 --> 00:00:27.394 line:5%,start
Listen, disco ball,
I'm not talking to you today.

00:00:27.460 --> 00:00:28.294 line:5%,start
-Move along.
-Oh, my God.

00:00:28.361 --> 00:00:29.829 line:5%,start
ABBY: <i>Coming up on </i>Dance Moms,

00:00:29.896 --> 00:00:31.331 line:5%,start
I'm bringing in another member.

00:00:31.398 --> 00:00:33.166 line:5%,start
I don't think she's replacing Paige.

00:00:33.233 --> 00:00:34.367 line:5%,start
She just did.

00:00:34.434 --> 00:00:35.502 line:5%,start
CHRISTI: <i>Chloe's crying.</i>

00:00:35.568 --> 00:00:36.803 line:5%,start
ABBY: I expect more from you.

00:00:36.870 --> 00:00:38.438 line:5%,start
What kind of parenting is that?

00:00:38.505 --> 00:00:40.807 line:5%,start
If you do good in that trio,
this 20 bucks is yours.

00:00:40.874 --> 00:00:42.575 line:5%,start
CHRISTI:
Don't you say that to my daughter!

00:00:42.642 --> 00:00:43.877 line:5%,start
ABBY: Look at the way that you act!

00:00:43.943 --> 00:00:45.111 line:5%,start
Be a role model!

00:00:45.178 --> 00:00:47.881 line:5%,start
<i>She came in here,</i>
<i>had this snotty little attitude,</i>

00:00:47.947 --> 00:00:49.249 line:5%,start
and you back her up.

00:00:50.316 --> 00:00:52.786 line:95%,end
(theme music playing)

